## Open Source Licence -

This project is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public Licence v3.0. The full licence text can be found in the AGPL-3.0 licence file in this repo or at [https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.en.html].

Under the AGPL-3.0, you are free to use, modify, and distribute this software, but you must also:

* Disclose the source code of your application.
* Distribute your application under the same AGPL-3.0 licence.
* Make the source code available to all users who interact with it over a network.

This is to ensure that any derivative works also remain open-source.

## Commercial License -

For projects where the terms of the AGPL-3.0 are not suitable, such as in proprietary or closed-source applications, we offer a separate commercial license.

The commercial license grants you the right to use this software in your applications without the copyleft restrictions of the AGPL-3.0. This means you are not required to disclose your source code.

To purchase a commercial license or for more information, please contact us at contact@uominnovationfactory.com.
